full_description: Spryfox is an AI company based in Darmstadt, Germany, founded six years ago by three engineers who wanted to build AI systems that actually ship. The team builds serious, production-grade solutions - LLM-based applications, predictive health systems, computer vision pipelines - solving real problems across industries like insurance, finance, and manufacturing. Small and focused, they pick the latest tools because they're the right ones, not because they're trendy. If you're a senior developer or ML engineer who wants to build things that matter with a team that actually understands the tech; they're hiring. Go talk to them.

